<p class="posted"><strong>Posted by <a href="mailto&#58;loral&#64;loralciriclight&#46;com">Loral</a> at September 10, 2004 01:42 PM</strong></p>
<p>Official flip flop:</p>

<p>Rytan - The scaling of the focus effects past 65 will effect all of the existing foci, although generally the higher end focus items have a higher max level then the lower tier focus effects. Generally the Elemental and time foci are capped at level 67, and the high end gates foci are capped at level 68. </p>

<p>So Elemental, Time, and GoD effects get a higher cap than normal focus 4 items.  Depending on the gear that we see in Omens this could either be good or bad.  Only time will tell.</p>


